settings.text:
Join us for a workshop this month at one of our New York City stores.
Enjoy an educational presentation and potting demonstration and choose a complimentary
plant pal to take home!
Birds Nest Fern is a great low maintenance little houseplant and a newbie here at Patch! Shes the perfect addition to a shelf or desk with her glossy coined shaped leaves.
Philodendron Scandens has been a main-stay in the houseplant team for generations, thanks mostly to his dramatic heart-shaped foliage.
